data.description: MOVE-IN READY PARTIAL FURNISHED! 4 BEDROOMS, 2.5 BATHS! This home is located in the highly desired Neigh board of Poinciana Village.  This beauty lay-out as Living/Dinning Room, family room and half bath on the first floor. All Bedrooms are upstairs, upgrade with walk-in closet and laundry room with washer and dryer included. New Roof on 2018! A large Fenced backyard, 2-car garages and extended driveway for additional parking space. This property is located minutes from public schools, shopping center, community center, bus stop and financial institutions. The Association of Poinciana Villages offer several parks, inground pool, aquatic center, fitness center and playgrounds. Submit your Offer today!
